org.opendaylight.controller.forwardingrulesmanager

Class PortGroupConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.configuration.ConfigurationObject
      • org.opendaylight.controller.forwardingrulesmanager.PortGroupConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PortGroupConfig
extends ConfigurationObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    PortGroupConfig class represents the User's Configuration with a Opaque Regular Expression String that is parsed and handled by PortGroupProvider. Typically, the opaque matchString will be a Regular Expression String supported by a particular PortGroupProvider based on Customer requirements.
    See Also:
